summary:
Kamallah Harris - After losing the election to Trump, Kamala Harris wandered into a mosque, seeking solace. As she prayed, a lightning bolt of inspiration struck. Emerging from the mosque, she declared, "Call me Kamallah Harris!" Ready to face the world with a fresh perspective, she joked, "Well, if you can't beat 'em, join 'em!" May God bless her next election victory

  -
